{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Chaiyaphum Province Stadium | image = | location = [[Chaiyaphum province|Chaiyaphum]], [[Thailand]] | coordinates = {{coord|15.807952| 102.020799|format=dms|type:landmark_scale:3000}} | opened = | owner = | operator = | surface = [[Grass]] | construction_cost = | former_names = | tenants = [[Chaiyaphum United F.C.|Mashare Chaiyaphum F.C.]] 2010-2011 | seating_capacity = 2,564 }}
'''Chaiyaphum Province Stadium''' ({{lang-th|สนาม จ.ชัยภูมิ}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Chaiyaphum Province]], [[Thailand]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Chaiyaphum United F.C.]]. The stadium holds 2,564 people.
