{{Refimprove|date=December 2014}} {{Use dmy dates|date=March 2014}} {{Use Indian English|date=June 2016}} {{Infobox Sport governing body |assocname= Haryana Archery Association |logo= |logosize= |sport= [[Archery]] |abbrev = (HAA) |founded = |region = [[Archery Association of India]] |regionyear = |headquarters = |location = [[Haryana]] |president = [[Abhimanyu Sindhu|Captain Abhimanyu Sindhu]] |chairman = |chiefexec = |secretary = |coach = |womenscoach = |replaced = |prevfounded = |url = |countryflag1=India }}
'''Haryana Archery Association ''' ('''HAA''') ({{lang-hi|हरियाणा तीरंदाजी संघ}}) is the state [[Sport governing body|governing body]] of [[archery]] in [[Haryana]]. It is a non-profit, government funded organisation under the [[Archery Association of India]]. '''HAA''' is affiliated to [[Archery Association of India]] and [[Haryana Olympic Association]]. Its current president is [[Abhimanyu Sindhu|Captain Abhimanyu Sindhu]].
