'''Indera SC''' is a [[association football|football]] club from [[Brunei]]. They won the [[Brunei Super League]] in [[2012–13 Brunei Super League|2013]]<ref>[http://rsssf.com/tablesb/brunei2013.html Brunei 2013] at RSSSF</ref> and [[2014 Brunei Super League|2014]]. They also won the [[Brunei FA Cup]] in 2018.<ref>{{cite web |title=Indera create history by winning DST FA Cup|url=https://borneobulletin.com.bn/indera-create-history-by-winning-dst-fa-cup/|date=2 April 2018|publisher=Borneo Bulletin|accessdate=3 April 2018}}</ref>

==Club Logo==

Its name having royal connotations, the colors in Indera's crest are those of the Bruneian royal family.<ref>https://www.fourfourtwo.com/sg/features/untold-stories-southeast-asian-clubs-indera-sc-brunei?page=0%2C1</ref>

